name: excel-add-in-insert-external-file
title: Insert an external Excel file and populate it with JSON data
shortDescription: This sample shows how to insert an existing template from an external Excel file into the currently open Excel file.
longDescription: Use insertWorksheetsFromBase64 to insert a worksheet from another Excel file into the open Excel file. Get JSON data and add it to the worksheet.

thumbnails.alt: Diagram showing the sample inserting an external spreadsheet into the existing spreadsheet.

references.name: insertWorksheetsFromBase64
references.description: Inserts the specified worksheets from a source workbook into the current workbook.
